text: Kevin Fisher (born 27 March 1995) is a British Virgin Islands international footballer who plays college soccer in the United States for Otero Junior College, as a striker. ==Career== Fisher played club football for Islanders FC, before playing college soccer with Otero Junior College. He made his international debut for the British Virgin Islands in 2014. ==References== Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:British Virgin Islands footballers Category:British Virgin Islands international footballers Category:Islanders FC players Category:Association football forwards Category:British Virgin Islands expatriate footballers Category:British Virgin Islands expatriates in the United States Category:Expatriate soccer players in the United States
